Shadowmere -- Prism Archive, Founding Precedent

Shadowmere is the reason the founding charter exists. Not the only
reason -- but the working demonstration of every principle Kiess
was built to reject. When Three-Power Governance debates whether a
policy has gone too far, someone says: "Check Shadowmere."

