Runoff routed through burial districts. Alchemical disposal entering
water channels. The blight is infrastructure memory. The Temple
Circle recognizes this from the Ashfall: canals dug for order became
channels distributing poison. Infrastructure built for order
becomes infrastructure that distributes catastrophe.

